Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 13:51:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(workspace): shell with tab navigation and settings

- workspace.store.ts: ephemeral tab state (inbox/contacts/communities/settings)
- TabBar: bottom navigation, active state, aria-current
- WorkspaceHeader: view title + avatar with static presence dot
- InboxView / ContactsView / CommunitiesView: designed empty states with
  Phase 2/3 CTAs (disabled until backend)
- SettingsView: functional - profile card, live public/private visibility
  switching (persisted), sign out, version footer
- EmptyState added to UI kit
- WorkspaceScreen recomposed as shell (header + view + tabs)
